{
  "stem": "2004.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I worked there until-- of course, we got married in August of 1950-- August 18, 1950.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was working-- I continued working until late in 1951.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "By the late of 1951, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Ann was already-- I think, we made a decision that I have to go into business for myself.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's no sense-- I mean, after all, I'm working for somebody a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How long can you work for somebody?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You've got to be in business for yourself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I made the decision to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went shopping for machinery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And whatever money we had, we bought-- I bought used machinery, old machinery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my first shop was I rented a basement in Manhattan, which was sort of-- it wasn't a basement-- it was a basement, but it was an open basement.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't even big enough for me to put a sign out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to  a sign painter, painted signs, bought machinery, bought tools, and started making furniture.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One of my first clients was a psychiatrist, who until even recently-- I, I spoke to him recently because he's sort of now retiring, and we spoke about he's moving to Florida and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But and of course, I started building up a business from-- hand-- sort of-- it was a matter of word of mouth at the time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And until I built up a clientele-- and I've built up a considerable clientele over 40, 40-somewhat years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Some of my customers are quite noted people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Cyrus Vance is one of them, the former Secretary of State.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I did work for, for-- he was a-- I did some works for people in show business.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
